# shine-links ✦

Cartoon shine sweep for links. Drop in one script tag, done.

## Via CDN (no install)

```html
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/shine-links/shine.js"></script>
```

## Via npm

```bash
npm install shine-links
```

```js
import "shine-links";
```

## Usage

Just add the class `shine` to any element:

```html
<a class="shine" href="#">Documentation</a>
```

Or apply to all links at once in JS:

```js
document.querySelectorAll("a").forEach(el => el.classList.add("shine"));
```

That's it.

